description:
This is a 40 minute workout called '40 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT || At-Home Pilates' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Enjoy this 40-Minute Full Body Pilates Workout that will sculpt and tone your entire body. This at-home pilates class will have you feeling stronger, energised and leave you with a post-workout glow! Let me know you go in the comments below. xx
